  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601790/extras/b951289c8c6c365473c7a7befc4edbdd.poster.avif?t=1619787906\" width=620 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601790/extras/b951289c8c6c365473c7a7befc4edbdd.webm?t=1619787906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601790/extras/b951289c8c6c365473c7a7befc4edbdd.mp4?t=1619787906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Welcome to Mini Island!</strong><br><br>Mini Island: Summer is a one small hold & Gun, boss Rush mini-game of Casual difficulty!<br>This beautiful place was built only for simple fun! Choose the character and difficulty level that best suits you and enjoy a short, simple but colorful boss rush minigame!<br><br><strong>More About & Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Casual difficulty<br></li><li> Hold & Gun and Boss Rush<br></li><li> Simple Hit & Dodge Style Action.<br></li><li> 4 types of 16 playable characters.<br></li><li> 7 stages with 26 boss fights.<br></li><li> Colorful and sparkling art graphics.<br></li><li> 20 minutes to 35 minutes playtime</li></ul>",
